title: 11/01 Fantasy Football Podcast: Kelvin, Legitometer, Fantasy Feud!
description:
Fun show for you today as we give you our favorite buy low (1:56) and sell high candidates (2:50). Find out why Heath loves Doug Martin going forward and what Jamey would be looking for if he sold Will Fuller ... Discussing the Fantasy impact of the Kelvin Benjamin trade (9:54). Devin Funchess or Benjamin rest of season? Cam Newton or Tyrod Taylor? Also, Adam is disgusted by a popular Halloween candy (20:30), we preview BUF-NYJ (30:36) and we deploy the Legitometer on Alex Smith (36:42), Marvin Jones (39:30), Aaron Jones (47:01), Jerick McKinnon (48:30) and many more ... Let's play Fantasy Feud (49:08)! Jamey and Heath go head-to-head! ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
